{"tid":539131,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗養殖場件事反映到香港人有幾咁本末倒置","createTime":"2018-01-24T09:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T14:21:37.000Z","uid":147376,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ce0ad0e59e7f2968fabf92ddbe192e4de0dae1d1","tid":539131,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T09:42:04.000Z","msg":"點解會有人撐賣瀕危動物個班人？佢地透過非法手段走私動物入香港，仲係野外放籠捉穿山甲<br />\n<br />\n佢地養得好就應該支持？咁將d人由原本住嘅地方捉去集中營，然後養得佢地肥肥白白就係值得鼓勵？最搞笑有d人話佢地係保育瀕危動物! 保乜撚野育，保育動物係將健康嘅動物繁殖，野放係一個安全，經評估動物可以生存並可持續發展嘅環境，繁殖個班人有無評估過環境之後將動物野放呀？冇不特止，仲攞佢地黎買賣，你點知賣畀個條友識唔識養，養死咗有點？有無跟進？<br />\n仲有將動物由其他地方運到禁止買賣佢地嘅香港已經係不負責任，因為你唔可以合法地擁有動物，當畀人發現時，動物就會受影響，咁你地班繁殖者咁做負責嘅表現咩？<br />\n<br />\n睇住而家d盲毛屌返愛協，漁護真係得啖笑(雖然佢地都係仆街)<br />\n<br />\n大家要諗清楚，邊d人先係令到d動物咁慘，唔到本末倒置"},{"pid":"e26bbc3ef2f2760fe6dca9173f6d577a8615d4b5","tid":539131,"uid":147376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T09:55:52.000Z","msg":"on 9留言<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/175017_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F175017_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=22845132&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/175144_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F175144_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ce928dfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/175531_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F175531_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=26491cfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/175540_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%